                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; names of the king, patriarch and
                           metropolitan; names of the donors; on fol. 5r and on the incipit page of
                           each Anaphora, a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines);
                           incipits and headings of some of the constituent texts; abbreviations;
                           some of the marginal notes (s. Varia); elements of the punctuation signs;
                           elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
